[2] USA (New York); Goldman Sachs
Date: Mon 30 Apr 2018
Source: Dealbreaker [edited]
https://dealbreaker.com/2018/04/mumps-outbreak-on-trading-floor-has-goldman-sachs-traders-wondering-which-of-the-seven-seals-this-one-is/

Traders in Bankers Goldman Sachs infected with Mumps
----------------------------------------------------
Goldman Sachs is battling to contain a rare but contagious flare-up of mumps after a few employees contracted the disease. Employees on one of its trading floors showed signs of the disease this week and the firm told people to get shots or visit the firm's health center if they didn't receive the vaccine during childhood, according to a person with knowledge of the matter who asked to remain anonymous discussing internal conditions....-more

